=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains details about the storage configuration of the knowledge base
in Redis Enterprise Cloud. For more information, see Create a vector
index in Redis Enterprise Cloud
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/bedrock/latest/userguide/knowledge-base-setup-oss.html).

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> CredentialsSecretArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the secret that you created in
Secrets Manager that is linked to your Redis Enterprise Cloud database.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Endpoint => Str

The endpoint URL of the Redis Enterprise Cloud database.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> FieldMapping => L<Paws::BedrockAgent::RedisEnterpriseCloudFieldMapping>

Contains the names of the fields to which to map information about the
vector store.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> VectorIndexName => Str

The name of the vector index.



